
// Create a Hyperlambda snippet that signals the [magic.ai.get-context] slot, passing the values of [.arguments] nodes named [type], [prompt], [threshold], [max_context_tokens], and [api_key] respectively as arguments named [type], [prompt], [threshold], [max_tokens], and [api_key].
signal:magic.ai.get-context
   type:x:@.arguments/*/type
   prompt:x:@.arguments/*/prompt
   threshold:x:@.arguments/*/threshold
   max_tokens:x:@.arguments/*/max_context_tokens
   api_key:x:@.arguments/*/api_key
